    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/2ec697c9019983f031b13c3c5990213f.poster.avif?t=1770133271\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/2ec697c9019983f031b13c3c5990213f.webm?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/2ec697c9019983f031b13c3c5990213f.mp4?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摩卡，一只被宠坏了的猫，厌倦了宅在家中的生活，决定远走高飞，寻找冒险。然而，由于街头遭到了训犬师的威胁，他的旅行也因此陡增艰险。摩卡需要在失去自己最好的朋友，以及自己所拥有的一切之前，学会求生，以及珍视他抛在身后的往昔。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/e6e2935bea9970f24486f1e80bbaff55.poster.avif?t=1770133271\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/e6e2935bea9970f24486f1e80bbaff55.webm?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/e6e2935bea9970f24486f1e80bbaff55.mp4?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/c5fc8deffb1fadde93036b82d1e09847.poster.avif?t=1770133271\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/c5fc8deffb1fadde93036b82d1e09847.webm?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/c5fc8deffb1fadde93036b82d1e09847.mp4?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/4a7739795e10c072b73553b2c3fc3242.webp?t=1770133271\" width=600 height=27 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索美丽的水彩手绘世界。  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受经典动画电影的魅力。  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发掘友谊的力量。  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验五味杂陈的旅程。  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做一只猫。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/250707725e25af6b4ed2458f39fbcef5.poster.avif?t=1770133271\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/250707725e25af6b4ed2458f39fbcef5.webm?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/250707725e25af6b4ed2458f39fbcef5.mp4?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/4a7739795e10c072b73553b2c3fc3242.webp?t=1770133271\" width=600 height=27 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想知道游戏适不适合你么？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你有想过体验猫的生活么？  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你对手绘动画电影感兴趣吗？  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你喜欢沉浸于情感丰富的故事中吗？  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你喜欢流程短的游戏（游玩时间约为 1-2 小时）吗？ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你追求简单易懂，便于掌控的挑战么？.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那太好了！因为我们的游戏可以让你体验上述这一切，还有许多其他内容。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/2bd4ec9f44650bd6e65fcb2c4f65fb03.poster.avif?t=1770133271\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/2bd4ec9f44650bd6e65fcb2c4f65fb03.webm?t=1770133271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822240/extras/4a7739795e10c072b73553b2c3fc3242.webp?t=1770133271\" width=600 height=27 /></span></p>",
